"<guilabel>Podeljeni prikaz</guilabel> određuje da li je <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view\"><application>Dolphinov</application> prikaz</link> podeljen "
"po pokretanju ili ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show filter bar</guilabel> controls if the filter bar is shown on "
"startup or not. See the <link linkend=\"filter-files\">section on the filter "
"bar</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Filterska traka</guilabel> određuje da li se po pokretanju vidi "
"filterska traka. Više detalja potražite u <link linkend=\"filter-files"
"\">odeljku o filterskoj traci</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Editable location bar</guilabel> controls if the location bar "
#| "is in editable mode on startup. The bread crumb mode of the location bar "
#| "is used otherwise. See the <link linkend=\"location-bar\">section about "
#| "the location bar</link> for details about the two modes."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Make location bar editable</guilabel> controls if the location bar "
"is in editable mode on startup. The bread crumb mode of the location bar is "
"used otherwise. See the <link linkend=\"location-bar\">section about the "
"location bar</link> for details about the two modes."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Traka lokacije se može uređivati</guilabel> određuje da li će "
"traka lokacije biti u režimu uređivanja po pokretanju. U suprotnom će biti u "
"režimu mrvica. Detalje o ovim režimima potražite u <link linkend=\"location-"
"bar\">odeljku o traci lokacije</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Open new folders in tabs</guilabel> controls whether &dolphin; "
"should open a new folder in a new tab of the current instance when called "
"externally. If not enabled, the new folders will be opened in new instances "
"of &dolphin;. By default this option is enabled."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Show full path inside location bar</guilabel> is enabled, the "
"full path of the current location is shown in the bread crumb mode of the "
"location bar. Otherwise, a shortened version of the path is shown if it "
"begins with the path of one of the places in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Ako je popunjeno <guilabel>Puna putanja u traci lokacije</guilabel>, traka "
"lokacije u režimu mrvica navodi potpunu putanju tekuće lokacije. Inače se "
"navodi skraćena verzija putanje kada počinje jednim od mesta sa panela "
"<guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show full path in title bar</guilabel> makes it easy to "
"distinguish between files or folders with the same name in different folders."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the behavior of &dolphin;'s view "
"modes. The three view modes (Icons, Compact, and Details) are accessible via "
"the tab bar at the top."
msgstr ""
"Ova grupa sadrži postavke kojima se utiče na ponašanje "
"<application>Dolphinovih</application> režima prikaza. Trima režimima "
"prikaza pristupa se preko trake jezičaka na vrhu (<guilabel>ikonice</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>sažeto</guilabel>, i <guilabel>detalji</guilabel>)."

# rewrite-msgid: /preferences dialog/configuration dialog/
#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Icons View settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Snimak ekrana sa postavkama prikaza u ikonicama u <application>Dolphinovom</"
"application> dijalogu za podešavanje."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes Settings."
msgstr "Postavke režima prikaza."

# rewrite-msgid: /preferences dialog/configuration dialog/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Postavke režima prikaza u <application>Dolphinovom</application> dijalogu za "
"podešavanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common settings for all view modes"
msgstr "Zajedničke postavke za sve režime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "All three view modes have some common settings:"
msgstr "Za sva tri režima prikaza važe neke zajedničke postavke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sliders which control the size of the icons. The <guilabel>Default</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> sizes are used if previews are "
"disabled or enabled, respectively. Note that the icon size can be changed "
"easily with the zoom slider in the status bar if the corresponding option is "
"enabled in the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-statusbar"
"\"><quote>General</quote> section of the settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Klizači kojima se određuje veličina ikonica. Veličine "
"<guilabel>Podrazumevana:</guilabel> ili <guilabel>Pregled:</guilabel> "
"koriste se, redom, kada su pregledi isključeni ili uključeni. Primetite da "
"se veličina ikonica lako može menjati klizačem uveličanja u traci stanja, "
"ako je uključena odgovarajuća opcija u <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-"
"general-statusbar\">odeljku <guilabel>Opšte</guilabel></link> u postavkama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A setting for the font used in the view mode: either the system font or a "
"custom font can be chosen."
msgstr ""
"Postavka za font korišćen u režimima prikaza: može se izabrati ili sistemski "
"ili poseban font."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The other settings in the <guilabel>Text</guilabel> section which apply to "
"only one of the view modes are discussed below."
msgstr ""
"Ostale postavke u odeljku <guilabel>Tekst</guilabel> koje važe samo za "
"pojedine režime prikaza izložene su ispod."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikonice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Width</guilabel> controls the minimum width that is reserved for "
"the text of a file item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Širina:</guilabel> određuje najmanju širinu koja je dopuštena za "
"tekst stavke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum lines</guilabel> means maximum number of text lines below "
"the icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Najviše redova:</guilabel> zadaje najveći broj redova teksta ispod "
"ikonice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compact"
msgstr "Sažeto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum width</guilabel> controls the maximum width that is "
"reserved for the text of a file item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Najveća širina:</guilabel> određuje najveću širinu koja je "
"dopuštena za tekst stavke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Detalji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel> determines whether any folders that "
"have subfolders are displayed in a tree view, where the sub items can be "
"expanded by &LMB; clicking the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> icon and collapsed by "
"clicking the <guiicon>v</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Proširive fascikle</guilabel> određuje da li se fascikle sa "
"potfasciklama prikazuju u vidu stabla, tako da se podstavke mogu raširiti "
"levim klikom na ikonicu <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> a sažeti klikom na ikonicu "
"<guiicon>v</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Folder size</guilabel> allows defining the property to use for "
"sorting folders by their size. It is possible to sort folders by number of "
"items by choosing <guilabel>Show number of items</guilabel> or by the size "
"of the contents by choosing <guilabel>Show size of contents</guilabel>. The "
"recursion level can be limited, which can be useful to constrain unneeded "
"iterations in deep folder structures or on slow file systems. It is also "
"possible to disable displaying folder size by choosing <guilabel>Show no "
"size</guilabel> (which might improve performance in rare cases, however "
"impacts other features like sorting)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Date style</guilabel> option can be used to configure the mode "
"to display dates in &dolphin;. It is possible to choose between "
"<guilabel>Relative</guilabel> (&eg;, <quote>Yesterday, 3:00pm</quote>) or "
"<guilabel>Absolute</guilabel> (&eg;, <quote>2020-12-23 15:00</quote>)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control how navigation in the folder "
"structure and in archives works."
msgstr ""
"Ova grupa postavki određuje kako radi kretanje kroz strukturu fascikli i "
"kroz arhive."

# rewrite-msgid: /preferences dialog/configuration dialog/
#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
