#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Folder View Properties"
msgid "Folder View Display Style"
msgstr "Svojstva prikaza fascikle"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following settings control how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
"the &dolphin; view, and are stored on a per-folder basis by default:"
msgstr ""
"Naredne postavke određuju kako se sadržaj fascikle prikazuje u "
"<application>Dolphinu</application>, i podrazumevano se skladište zasebno za "
"svaku fasciklu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid "The view mode (Icons, Compact, Details)"
msgstr "Režim prikaza (ikonice, sažeto, detalji)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sorting of items, which is determined by the sort order (ascending, "
"descending) and the attribute (such as name, size,...) that the items are "
"sorted by"
msgstr ""
"Ređanje stavki, određeno redosledom (rastuće, opadajuće) i atributom (ime, "
"veličina...) po kojem se ređa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
