"guilabel> tab of &dolphin;'s General settings</link>) or not?"
msgstr ""
"Pregledi — da li se prikazuju umesto ikonica (na osnovu postavki pod <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-previews\">jezičkom <guilabel>Pregledi</"
"guilabel> u <application>Dolphinovom</application> opštim postavkama</link>)?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are items shown in groups in the views?"
msgstr "Da li su stavke grupisane u prikazima?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are hidden files shown?"
msgstr "Da li se vide skriveni fajlovi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What additional information (besides the name) is shown in the Icons or "
